title: Inside Kendall Jenner’s Cozy L.A. Hideaway

constellations_other.name: Raemar, rap and reality TV
constellations_other.description: James Turrell's immersive artworks have an unusual connection with Saturday Night Live, hip hop and reality TV royalty.

description: Kendall Jenner welcomes Architecture Digest for a tour of her serene LA home. Just off the entry, a signature James Turrell ovoid wall sculpture greets visitors with a dreamy chromatic display, the first of many personal artistic accents woven throughout her home.
